    "ss_faq_5_EgGmkP": {
      "type": "ss-faq-5",
      "blocks": {
        "item_JJB7w8": {
          "type": "item",
          "name": "Features",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Features",
            "answer": "<p><strong>Create Custom Clothing Together—No Experience Needed</strong><br/>Ninja Pressables Packs are themed collections of kid-friendly designs that make customizing clothing a fun and creative family activity. Each pack includes a variety of playful graphics that parents and children can apply together using a household iron or heat press. Whether you're decorating t-shirts, hoodies, or tote bags, it's a simple, mess-free way to bond and bring your kids' favorite designs to life.</p><p><strong>Apply It To Almost Anything</strong><br/>Pajamas, jerseys, jackets—you name it! Ninja Pressables work on nearly any fabric or color, making it easy to decorate all your favorite clothes.</p><p><strong>Bright Colors, Big Smiles</strong><br/>Our advanced printing captures even the tiniest lines and colorful details, so every design looks just as your child imagined—bold, vibrant, and full of personality.</p><p><strong>Just Press and Go</strong><br/>Kids choose their designs, place them just right, and tape them down. A grown-up does the ironing, but the best part is theirs: peeling back the film to reveal the finished creation. It’s an easy, hands-on project the whole family can enjoy together.</p><p><strong>Comfy and Kid-Approved</strong><br/>Ninja Pressables feel soft and smooth—not stiff like vinyl or other methods—so kids can wear their creations comfortably all day long.</p><p><strong>Made to Last (Even After 100 Washes!)</strong><br/>Built for real life, these transfers hold up through over 100 washes—staying bright, bold, and ready for whatever your kids get into.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_tgGUWh": {
          "type": "item",
          "name": "Application & Care Instructions",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Application & Care Instructions",
            "answer": "<p>Click <a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/pages/ninja-crafts-pressing-instructions\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>here</strong></span></a> to watch our Ninja Crafts Pressing Instructions Tutorial Video.</p><p>Follow these simple steps to ensure your Ninja Crafts Pressables get the best results:</p><p><strong>1. Position Your Design<br/></strong><br/>Line up your artwork on the t-shirt or fabric where you want it placed. To keep the design from shifting, secure it with the included heat-resistant tape.</p><p><strong>2. Press with Household Iron (Adult Only)<br/></strong><br/>Set your iron to the highest heat that matches your fabric type and turn off the steam. If the design isn’t adhering, increase toward the cotton/linen setting (or the hottest setting) without damaging the fabric. Cover the design with the included Protective Parchment Paper and press firmly for about 15-20 seconds.</p><p><strong>3. Peel After a Few Seconds<br/></strong><br/>Wait a few seconds until its cool to the touch, then carefully peel the transfer sheet away. If parts of the design haven’t stuck, lay it back down and press again with a bit more pressure or slightly more heat until it adheres.</p><p><strong>4. Optional Step - Final Press & Finish<br/></strong><br/>Place the Protective Parchment Paper back over the design and press again for about 15 seconds. This softens the finish, improves durability, and removes shine.</p><p><strong>5. Care and Washing<br/></strong><br/>It is always recommended to wash any fabric with Pressables designs inside out to protect the design from being damaged by other items in the washer/dryer.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_8HG3bM": {
          "type": "item",
          "name": "Shipping & Returns",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Shipping & Returns",
            "answer": "<p>Orders over $75 of Pressables and supplies will automatically qualify for <strong>Free Shipping</strong>. Express shipping options as fast as 1 Business Day available at checkout. For Canadian customers, orders of $99+ will qualify for Free Shipping.</p><p>Read our <a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/pages/shipping-policy\">Shipping Policy</a> for more information.</p><p><strong>Refunds & Reprints</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/pages/contact\" target=\"_blank\">Contact us</a> within 45 days of receiving your order to submit a request for a refund or reprint. We will reprint any order where there is a print quality or adherence issue. If you'd like a refund or reprint for another reason, it must be approved by management first.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_ymJ6YM": {
          "type": "item",
          "name": "Full Details",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Full Details",
            "answer": "<p>Ninja Pressables Packs make it easy for parents and kids to create custom clothing together—no experience needed. Each pack includes playful designs that press onto almost any fabric with a household iron. The prints are vibrant, soft to the touch, and built to last over 100 washes. No gluing, no mess—just fun, fast, and kid-approved creativity.</p><p><strong>Adult Supervision Required</strong>: This product is intended for use by adults or with adult supervision. Children should not handle heat press or ironing equipment.</p><p><strong>Heat Hazard</strong>: Applying Pressables involves high temperatures. Only adults should operate heat presses or irons to prevent burns or injury. Always use heat presses and irons according to the manufacturer’s instructions. Work on a stable, flat, heat tolerant surface. After pressing, allow both the equipment and the transfer to cool completely before touching or moving.</p><p><strong>Choking Hazard</strong>: Small pieces may present a choking hazard. Not suitable for children under 3 years.</p><p><strong>Material Safety</strong>: Transfers are made with materials compliant with CPSIA safety standards. If you have specific allergies or sensitivities, test a small area before full application.</p><p><strong>Proper Use Only</strong>: Use Pressables only as directed. Misuse may result in injury or damage to surfaces.</p><p><strong>Liability</strong>: The manufacturer and seller assume no responsibility for injuries or damages resulting from misuse or unsupervised use.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
